" key repeat hack for resizing splits
nmap <c-w>+ <c-w>+<sid>ws
nmap <c-w>- <c-w>-<sid>ws
nmap <c-w>> <c-w>><sid>ws
nmap <c-w>< <c-w><<sid>ws
